\fI?GL_TEXTURE_COMPRESSION_HINT\fR\&: \fIParams\fR\& returns a single value indicating the mode of the texture compression hint\&. The initial value is \fI?GL_DONT_CARE\fR\&\&.
.LP
\fI?GL_TEXTURE_BUFFER_BINDING\fR\&: \fIParams\fR\& returns a single value, the name of the texture buffer object currently bound\&. The initial value is 0\&. See \fBgl:bindBuffer/2\fR\& \&.
