\fI?GL_UNSIGNED_SHORT_5_6_5_REV\fR\& unsigned 16-bit integer with reversed component ordering 
.br
\fI?GL_UNSIGNED_SHORT_4_4_4_4\fR\& unsigned 16-bit integer 
