\fI?GL_UNSIGNED_INT_10_10_10_2\fR\& unsigned 32-bit integer 
.br
\fI?GL_UNSIGNED_INT_2_10_10_10_REV\fR\& unsigned 32-bit integer with reversed component ordering 
