.LP
\fIgl:copyTexImage1D\fR\& defines a one-dimensional texture image with pixels from the current \fI?GL_READ_BUFFER\fR\&\&.
.LP
The screen-aligned pixel row with left corner at (x y) and with a length of width+2(border) defines the texture array at the mipmap level specified by \fILevel\fR\& \&. \fIInternalformat\fR\& specifies the internal format of the texture array\&.
.LP
