.LP
If any of the pixels within the specified row of the current \fI?GL_READ_BUFFER\fR\& are outside the window associated with the current rendering context, then the values obtained for those pixels are undefined\&.
.LP
\fIgl:copyTexImage1D\fR\& defines a one-dimensional texture image with pixels from the current \fI?GL_READ_BUFFER\fR\&\&.
