.LP
\fIgl:mapGrid\fR\& and \fBgl:evalMesh1/3\fR\& are used together to efficiently generate and evaluate a series of evenly-spaced map domain values\&. \fBgl:evalMesh1/3\fR\& steps through the integer domain of a one- or two-dimensional grid, whose range is the domain of the evaluation maps specified by \fBgl:map1d/6\fR\& and \fBgl:map1d/6\fR\& \&.
