In addition to the errors generated by \fIgl:bindFragDataLocation\fR\&, the program \fIProgram\fR\& will fail to link if:
.LP
The number of active outputs is greater than the value \fI?GL_MAX_DRAW_BUFFERS\fR\&\&.
