.LP
\fIgl:bindVertexArray\fR\& binds the vertex array object with name \fIArray\fR\& \&. \fIArray\fR\& is the name of a vertex array object previously returned from a call to \fBgl:genVertexArrays/1\fR\& , or zero to break the existing vertex array object binding\&.
