.LP
Retrieve the index of a named uniform block
.LP
\fIgl:getUniformIndices\fR\& retrieves the indices of a number of uniforms within \fIProgram\fR\& \&.
.LP
\fIProgram\fR\& must be the name of a program object for which the command \fBgl:linkProgram/1\fR\& must have been called in the past, although it is not required that \fBgl:linkProgram/1\fR\& must have succeeded\&. The link could have failed because the number of active uniforms exceeded the limit\&.
.LP
