.LP
If \fIPname\fR\& is \fI?GL_UNIFORM_BLOCK_BINDING\fR\&, then the index of the uniform buffer binding point last selected by the uniform block specified by \fIUniformBlockIndex\fR\& for \fIProgram\fR\& is returned\&. If no uniform block has been previously specified, zero is returned\&.
.LP
