\fI?GL_TEXTURE_COMPARE_FUNC\fR\&: Returns a single-valued texture comparison function, a symbolic constant\&. The initial value is \fI?GL_LEQUAL\fR\&\&. See \fBgl:samplerParameteri/3\fR\& \&.
